    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay that makes sense. but the way it's written here, it says i have to indemnify them against any third-party copyright claims. so like, if someone else claims i used their work even if i didn't, i'm the one paying for everything? thats what im worried about. is that normal to see in these types of contracts?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
